high_descs: Take a  couple steps to your left to face a coffee mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the fridge that's on the right and stand and face it.
Cool the mug down in the freezer and take it out and close the freezer door.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the mug in the right hand sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in the fridge.

high_descs: Go straight and to the left to the kitchen island.
Take the mug from the kitchen island.
Turn right, go forward a little, turn right to face the fridge.
Put the mug on the lowest level of the top compartment of the fridge. Close then open the fridge door. Take the mug from the fridge.
Turn around, go straight all the way to the counter to the left of the sink, turn right to face the sink.
Put the mug in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and take two steps before turning to the right to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the cup on the edge of the center island.
Turn to the right and take two steps then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the cup on the shelf next to the lettuce, then close the fridge door for three seconds, then open the fridge and take the cup out.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
